==English==

===Etymology===
From [[donation]] + [[ware]] a contraction of [[software]]

===Noun===
'''donationware'''

#{{cattag|Internet}} A variant of [[freeware]] that offers an option to its user to donate money to the program's author. In cases where the request to donate money is nags the user, this is called [[nagware]].

